# Raycast configuration
# Raycast is configured through its UI - this module is for documentation
#
# Setup steps:
# 1. Open Raycast, go to Settings (Cmd+,)
# 2. Set hotkey to Cmd+Space (will prompt to disable Spotlight shortcut)
# 3. Recommended extensions to install:
#    - Clipboard History
#    - GitHub
#    - Brew
#    - Kill Process
#    - Color Picker
#    - Emoji Search
#    - Calculator
#    - File Search
#    - System Commands
#    - Speedtest
#    - Tailscale
# 4. Disable "Window Management" extension (using Aerospace instead)
# 5. Consider syncing settings via Raycast Cloud
